# Activate your virtual environment first
.venv\Scripts\activate

# Then run scripts in order:
python src/01_eda.py
python src/02_eda_visualizations.py
python src/03_feature_engineering.py
python src/04_preprocessing.py
python src/05_modelling.py
python src/04b_baseline_models.py   # needs 05 to run first (loads saved models)
python src/05b_threshold_tuning.py  # needs 05 to run first
Key things to remember:

Always run from the project root (capstone 491/project/), not from inside src/ — otherwise the data/, models/, plots/ paths won't resolve
Run in order — each script depends on outputs from the previous one:

01 → 02 → 03 → 04 → 05 → 04b / 05b
04b and 05b both load models saved by 05, so 05 must run before them
